Package edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.dhalmy.domain

Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.dhalmy.domain.Employee
  • @Entity
public class Employee
extends Object
    Represents an employee within the organization. Each employee is uniquely identified by an ID and has attributes such as first name, last name, username, hire date, department, and associated assets like laptops and cubicles.
    Author:
    David
